data.description: Assumable VA Loan @ 2.5%, or Up to $11k in buy-down points! In the gated community of Chanan Estates South of I-10 the home backs up to a pond and trail. Built in 2o22 this home has already received many upgrades. Key Features Include:Solar Panels, Whole Home Air Purifier, Whole Home Water Filter & Softener, Privacy Fence, Shed, 3 Car Garage, Open Kitchen w/ Granite Breakfast Bar, Shaker White Cabinets Accented w/ Crown Molding, French Gray Porcelain Plank Tile,10' Ceilings, Separate Dining & Breakfast Nook.Gorgeous master suite fitted with tray ceiling & back-lit crown molding, his & hers walk-in closets w/built-in shelving, double vanity, tiled shower w/ Topaz Pebble floor, & oversized soaking tub.The large bonus room upstairs is perfect for your home office! Buyer to verify info.
